1
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:09,670
♪Unknowingly, my gaze falls on you♪

2
00:00:09,930 --> 00:00:12,550
♪Your eyes are filled with starlight♪

3
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:15,850
♪Yet only my reflection remains♪

4
00:00:18,550 --> 00:00:21,020
♪The warm sea breeze kisses you♪

5
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:23,840
♪Longing holds my breath still♪

6
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:27,760
♪My heart is quietly unwavering♪

7
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:33,230
♪This feeling, in silence♪

8
00:00:34,210 --> 00:00:38,020
♪Circles the path of the stars♪

9
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:41,620
=Ten Years of Unrequited Love=

10
00:00:41,660 --> 00:00:45,580
=Episode 7=

11
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,800
Weren't you hiding this
from Chairman Cen?

12
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:53,320
Why are you telling me?

13
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:56,240
In your eyes,

14
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,280
I'm just someone driven by gain.

15
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,280
Aren't you afraid I might betray you?

16
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:07,920
♪I wouldn't have felt
the warmth of light♪

17
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:12,960
♪Falling softly from my fingertips♪

18
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:18,290
♪If not for the night♪

19
00:01:18,710 --> 00:01:23,450
♪Always wrapped in darkness♪

20
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,440
Betray me?

21
00:01:29,210 --> 00:01:34,610
♪Watch the sea and stars run wild♪

22
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:35,650
You won't.

23
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,280
Don't be so sure of yourself.

24
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,800
The evidence has been found.

25
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,840
I'm off duty now.

26
00:01:48,270 --> 00:01:52,950
♪If you hadn't happened to pass by♪

27
00:01:53,540 --> 00:01:58,500
♪If I hadn't been half asleep♪

28
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:03,840
♪If the rain hadn't poured down♪

29
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:07,270
♪If the wind hadn't suddenly stirred♪

30
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,200
Betray me?

31
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,880
You won't.

32
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:12,160
You're driving today.

33
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,160
Don't wear high heels.

34
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:15,560
Aren't heels more formal?

35
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,240
With me, comfort comes first.

36
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,040
If I recall correctly,

37
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,120
today is your birthday.

38
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,960
If she asks you to pick

39
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,160
between us or raises tricky questions,

40
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,560
I can't take the blame for that.

41
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,560
I'd choose you.

42
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,320
Over these ten years,

43
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,960
how many women have you slept with?

44
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,440
You know my reputation,

45
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,000
don't you?

46
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,080
Isn't this truth or dare?

47
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,800
Why did you stop asking?

48
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,440
Go on, ask me.

49
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:54,240
Ask me, and I'll answer.

50
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,360
Ask me. I can tell you.

51
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,800
- Miaomiao.
- Just ask me.

52
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,720
You're drunk.

53
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:03,810
♪I wouldn't have felt
the warmth of light♪

54
00:03:04,490 --> 00:03:08,880
♪Falling softly from my fingertips♪

55
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:14,260
♪If not for the night♪

56
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:16,990
♪Always wrapped in darkness♪

57
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,040
It's settled now.

58
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,080
The situation has turned around.

59
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,800
Weiyang's scheme to smear Mirui

60
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,240
is already trending online.

61
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,760
Good news.

62
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,880
- Miaomiao.
- What's wrong?

63
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,720
The online opinion has shifted now.

64
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,740
Everyone says it's Weiyang's scheme

65
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:37,720
to tarnish Mirui's name.

66
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:38,720
It's trending online.

67
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,790
- Really?
- Yes.

68
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,790
Let me take a look.

69
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:42,920
This is finally settled.

70
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,800
We've been exhausted these days.

71
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,080
That's wonderful.

72
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:47,480
What do you want to eat?

73
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,540
Let's have dinner together.

74
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,120
- You're treating us?
- Yes.

75
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,680
Then I must pick a good restaurant.

76
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,920
Let's have

77
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,960
hotpot.

78
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,360
Let's go for hotpot.

79
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,400
Miaomiao?

80
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,120
Sounds good.

81
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,560
Mr. Chang.

82
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,360
The crisis statement is already out.

83
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,020
But we still can't calm things down.

84
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,800
We're trying to reach the Maiji Team.

85
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,640
No matter the cost,

86
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,640
solve this as fast as you can.

87
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,120
However,

88
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,520
the rumors online...

89
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,240
Then figure something out.

90
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,800
Go then.

91
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,640
Alright.

92
00:05:14,820 --> 00:05:15,920
What are you thinking about?

93
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,880
You seem distracted.

94
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,600
I'm not.

95
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,320
Thank you.

96
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,890
♪Kept my troubles inside♪

97
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,720
Stop taking

98
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,080
all the burden on yourself.

99
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,520
Even if the sky falls on Mirui,

100
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:31,240
others will bear it.

101
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,520
You won't be affected.

102
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,080
If you ever need anything,

103
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,600
just come and talk to me anytime.

104
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,580
Thank you.

105
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,600
Mr. Cen, I don't need it.

106
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,800
Thank you.

107
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,920
You do need it.

108
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,200
Take me somewhere.

109
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,920
Where to?

110
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,160
To Su Peipei's place.

111
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,360
What are you waiting for?

112
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,440
Let's go.

113
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:21,900
(Elevator Lobby)

114
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,760
Mr. Cen, you change cars fast.

115
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,840
Take it.

116
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,280
This is for you.

117
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,000
Cen Siyuan.

118
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,440
Don't use your tricks on other girls

119
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,600
on me.

120
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,480
I won't fall for that.

121
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,800
I bought you a car

122
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,840
so you can drive Peipei and me.

123
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,760
Cen Siyuan,

124
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,000
do you really feel no shame

125
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,560
treating me like your maid?

126
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,880
That's right.

127
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:55,840
If you have any thoughts, just tell me.

128
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,240
But it seems you don't.

129
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,840
So, do your job as our maid.

130
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,440
Handle your duties properly

131
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,720
to earn your bonus and insurance.

132
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,760
Hello, Chairman Cen.

133
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,560
Alright, let me check.

134
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:24,860
(Rising Star Su Peipei
Stands with Mirui)

135
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,640
(Comment)
Peipei looks stunning.

136
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,720
I want to drink with Peipei.

137
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,640
Mirui, Mirui.

138
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,800
Let's make memories just for us.

139
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,400
Goddess, I'll always believe in you.

140
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,840
What's wrong?

141
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,240
I bought the car.

142
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:01,640
Miss Su seems quite impressive.

143
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,600
She was just trending online.

144
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,600
To step up at a time like this

145
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,520
really takes a lot of courage.

146
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,600
You're on her side so soon?

147
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,040
Aren't you supposed to be on my side?

148
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,360
I'm only joking.

149
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,680
Have you got it?

150
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,360
Yes.

151
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,040
It's easy to offer help in good times;

152
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,280
it's hard when times are tough.

153
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,620
Mirui just made a bold comeback,

154
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:21,580
and her post appeared.

155
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,040
I have to say it's a good show.

156
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,320
All those years with me are worth it.

157
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,460
People online say all sorts of things.

158
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,520
Just ignore them.

159
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,520
I just want Siyuan to know

160
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,280
my feelings for him are true.

161
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,360
You're always thinking about love.

162
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,320
All your focus is on him alone.

163
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,800
His mother doesn't even like you.

164
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:42,640
What if he changes his heart one day?

165
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,180
Wouldn't that be a big loss for you?

166
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,320
If you ask me,

167
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,200
it's better to break up with him.

168
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,120
Right now, you're a rising star.

169
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,840
Your career should come first.

170
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,800
But I really like him.

171
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,640
After we returned home,

172
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,680
he hasn't even touched me.

173
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,280
Do you think he's...

174
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,200
Hello.

175
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,720
You are Su Peipei, right?

176
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:07,640
I am Cen Siyuan's mother.

177
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:29,000
♪The moon hides in the dusk♪

178
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,720
♪Kept my troubles inside♪

179
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,720
♪Snowflakes drift like clouds♪

180
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,640
♪Mingling into the river of dreams♪

181
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:43,040
♪Each of our frames♪

182
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:46,280
♪Bittersweet memories linger♪

183
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:51,800
♪Meeting you broke my lonely drift♪

184
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:58,480
♪The cloud kisses the sea,
gently expressing love♪

185
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:05,360
♪Sunset lingers in your eyes,
refusing to leave♪

186
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:12,000
♪I borrow the wind to hold you close♪

187
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:15,800
♪Wherever my gaze falls♪

188
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:21,280
♪All I want is to follow you♪
